962
00:58:27,840 --> 00:58:28,920
 Pa divno.

963
00:58:28,920 --> 00:58:30,320
 Tako da evo, petero nas je.

964
00:58:30,320 --> 00:58:32,320
 Petero, dakle četvero,

965
00:58:33,240 --> 00:58:35,200
