967
00:58:36,260 --> 00:58:39,980
 Pa, mislim, ponosni.

968
00:58:39,980 --> 00:58:43,300
 Ja smatram da je Božji dar.

969
00:58:43,300 --> 00:58:44,560
 Mislim, nije teško,

970
00:58:44,560 --> 00:58:46,400
